HEADWORD: Subindication
<hw>Sub*in`di*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
indicating by signs; a slight indication.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>subindication</xex> and shadowing of heavenly
things.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Barrow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
